data.description: This lovely corner lot is home to a cute 3 bedroom 2 bath cabin on over one half acre of land just a five minute drive to the historic town of Creede, Colorado. This mountain home in Valley Vista Estates has seen a facelift of late with more to come! The exterior has been resided, new back deck, engineered, oak/ mahogany floors in the living room, new refrigerator and dishwasher ,and coming at the end of January, is a brand spanking new kitchen with hickory cabinets, granite counters and all new plumbing. Entering the cabin from the back porch you enter into a large mud/ laundry room with tile floors. The dining area and kitchen flow seamlessly to the living area. The dining room has a sliding glass door with access to a nice deck for enjoying the views of the pinnacles above Creede.  Rounding out the home are two bedrooms and a bath and the primary bedroom with its private bath. This cabin is perfect for year round living, second home or even short or long term rental.
